    "description": {
      "content": "Access to US African Development Foundation (USADF) grant opportunity listings through the Grants.gov API. USADF posts open grant solicitations on Grants.gov for African grassroots enterprises, cooperatives, social entrepreneurs, and community organizations seeking funding for African-led development initiatives. USADF uses agency code ADF on Grants.gov. This spec represents the USADF-relevant subset of the Grants.gov API.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Grants.gov Contact Center",
      "type": "text/plain"
    }
